snippet.title: The Wild Update: Where Will You Wander? – Official Minecraft Trailer
snippet.description: Run free and soak in the natural beauty of the mangrove swamps. The Wild Update introduces the allay, frogs, and tadpoles to the Overworld’s ecosystem. Discover the natural beauty of building with mangrove wood and mud blocks on June 7. Stay tuned to discover everything that’s coming in Minecraft 1.19!
